title: STAT+: Lawsuit against Hims & Hers should be ‘wake-up call’ for compounders, Novo chief counsel says
description: Novo's chief counsel says telehealth companies and compounding pharmacies that are continuing to make copycat versions of Wegovy “should be very, very much on notice.”
content: Novo's chief counsel says telehealth companies and compounding pharmacies that are continuing to make copycat versions of Wegovy “should be very, very much on notice.”
